et/rKuvQzsDiVcWKk73YtUk4h-320-80.png.webp 320w\" sizes=\"(min-width: 710px) 670px, calc(100vw - 30px)\"/\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/rKuvQzsDiVcWKk73YtUk4h-320-80.png\" alt=\"Scalloped Speckled Stoneware Dinner Plate, 26cm, Off White\" srcset=\"https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/rKuvQzsDiVcWKk73YtUk4h-1920-80.png 1920w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/rKuvQzsDiVcWKk73YtUk4h-1600-80.png 1600w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/rKuvQzsDiVcWKk73YtUk4h-1280-80.png 1280w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/rKuvQzsDiVcWKk73YtUk4h-1024-80.png 1024w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/rKuvQzsDiVcWKk73YtUk4h-768-80.png 768w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/rKuvQzsDiVcWKk73YtUk4h-415-80.png 415w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/rKuvQzsDiVcWKk73YtUk4h-360-80.png 360w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/rKuvQzsDiVcWKk73YtUk4h-320-80.png 320w\" sizes=\"(min-width: 710px) 670px, calc(100vw - 30px)\" loading=\"lazy\" data-original-mos=\"https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/rKuvQzsDiVcWKk73YtUk4h.png\" data-pin-media=\"https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/rKuvQzsDiVcWKk73YtUk4h.png\"/\u003e\u003c/picture\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\n\n\u003c/div\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003ch2 id=\"section-how-to-assemble-the-table\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003eHow to assemble the table\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/h2\u003e\u003cp\u003eIn the video, Bradley demonstrates how uses the No More Nails glue to stick the vases together with the plate glued on top.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003eNext, he pulled out his paints and using bold primary colours, painted the table a mix of blue, yellow and red.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cdiv data-hydrate=\"true\" id=\"slice-container-newsletterForm-articleInbodyContent-kbcLidvSJCBCVAjbrs58rd\"\u003e\u003csection\u003e\u003cp\u003eSign up to our newsletter for style and decor inspiration, house makeovers, project advice and more.\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/section\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003cp\u003eThe end result is simply gorgeous, and while it doesn’t look exactly like Mia Hamborg’s original, it\u0026#39;s certinaly an impressive piece. Especially given the total cost, as the two vases came to a combined cost of £16 and No More Nails glue can be bought for as little as £4.49 on Amazon.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003ePlus if you have an old plate at home and are wondering \u003ca data-analytics-id=\"inline-link\" href=\"https://www.idealhome.co.uk/diy/what-to-do-with-leftover-paint\" data-before-rewrite-localise=\"https://www.idealhome.co.uk/diy/what-to-do-with-leftover-paint\"\u003ewhat to do with leftover paint\u003c/a\u003e, then this project could kill a couple more birds with the one stone.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cdiv data-id=\"f4501978-e88f-4bc0-a58d-9646d999f4f7\"\u003e\n\u003ca href=\"https://www.awin1.com/awclick.php?awinmid=17021\u0026amp;awinaffid=103504\u0026amp;clickref=idealhome-gb-1083288594319833961\u0026amp;p=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.madeindesign.co.uk%2Fprod-shuffle-mh1-end-table-wood-multicoloured-wood-modular-o-45-x-h-69-cm-tradition-ref701031-trad.html%3Futm_source%3Dgoogle%26utm_medium%3Dcpc%26utm_content%3Dqid_gad_c19857459252_g_a%26utm_term%3D%26utm_id%3Dqid_gad_c19857459252_g_a%26utm_term%3D%26utm_campaign%3DUK%2520-%2520Pmax%2520-%2520Middle%2520-%2520Produits%2520-%2520PMAX%2520%26gad_source%3D1%26gclid%3DCjwKCAjwpbi4BhByEiwAMC8JncWweiPHgQbOZS0PeaTRhygPUot-GnV21jBMs0dRVeCqBJenr9foTxoCJYIQAvD_BwE#SHOP\" data-model-name=\"Shuffle Modular Table\" data-url=\"https://www.madeindesign.co.uk/prod-shuffle-mh1-end-table-wood-multicoloured-wood-modular-o-45-x-h-69-cm-tradition-ref701031-trad.html?utm_source=google\u0026amp;utm_medium=cpc\u0026amp;utm_content=qid_gad_c19857459252_g_a\u0026amp;utm_term=\u0026amp;utm_id=qid_gad_c19857459252_g_a\u0026amp;utm_term=\u0026amp;utm_campaign=UK%20-%20Pmax%20-%20Middle%20-%20Produits%20-%20PMAX%20\u0026amp;gad_source=1\u0026amp;gclid=CjwKCAjwpbi4BhByEiwAMC8JncWweiPHgQbOZS0PeaTRhygPUot-GnV21jBMs0dRVeCqBJenr9foTxoCJYIQAvD_BwE#SHOP\" target=\"_blank\" referrerpolicy=\"no-referrer-when-downgrade\" rel=\"sponsored noopener\" data-hl-processed=\"hawklinks\" data-placeholder-url=\"https://www.awin1.com/awclick.php?awinmid=17021\u0026amp;awinaffid=103504\u0026amp;clickref=hawk-custom-tracking\u0026amp;p=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.madeindesign.co.uk%2Fprod-shuffle-mh1-end-table-wood-multicoloured-wood-modular-o-45-x-h-69-cm-tradition-ref701031-trad.html%3Futm_source%3Dgoogle%26utm_medium%3Dcpc%26utm_content%3Dqid_gad_c19857459252_g_a%26utm_term%3D%26utm_id%3Dqid_gad_c19857459252_g_a%26utm_term%3D%26utm_campaign%3DUK%2520-%2520Pmax%2520-%2520Middle%2520-%2520Produits%2520-%2520PMAX%2520%26gad_source%3D1%26gclid%3DCjwKCAjwpbi4BhByEiwAMC8JncWweiPHgQbOZS0PeaTRhygPUot-GnV21jBMs0dRVeCqBJenr9foTxoCJYIQAvD_BwE#SHOP\" data-google-interstitial=\"false\" data-merchant-name=\"madeindesign.co.uk\" data-merchant-id=\"104381\" data-merchant-url=\"madeindesign.co.uk\" data-merchant-network=\"AW\"\u003e\u003cp data-bordeaux-image-check=\"\"\u003e\u003cpicture\u003e\u003csource type=\"image/webp\" srcset=\"https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/5is64ZLWFH2jHLc3fQE4o6-1920-80.jpg.webp 1920w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/5is64ZLWFH2jHLc3fQE4o6-1600-80.jpg.webp 1600w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/5is64ZLWFH2jHLc3fQE4o6-1280-80.jpg.webp 1280w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/5is64ZLWFH2jHLc3fQE4o6-1024-80.jpg.webp 1024w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/5is64ZLWFH2jHLc3fQE4o6-768-80.jpg.webp 768w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/5is64ZLWFH2jHLc3fQE4o6-415-80.jpg.webp 415w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/5is64ZLWFH2jHLc3fQE4o6-360-80.jpg.webp 360w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/5is64ZLWFH2jHLc3fQE4o6-320-80.jpg.webp 320w\" sizes=\"(min-width: 710px) 670px, calc(100vw - 30px)\"/\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/5is64ZLWFH2jHLc3fQE4o6-320-80.jpg\" alt=\"Shuffle Mh1 End Table Wood Multicoloured / Wood - Modular - Ø 45 X H 69 Cm - \u0026amp;tradition\" srcset=\"https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/5is64ZLWFH2jHLc3fQE4o6-1920-80.jpg 1920w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/5is64ZLWFH2jHLc3fQE4o6-1600-80.jpg 1600w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/5is64ZLWFH2jHLc3fQE4o6-1280-80.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/5is64ZLWFH2jHLc3fQE4o6-1024-80.jpg 1024w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/5is64ZLWFH2jHLc3fQE4o6-768-80.jpg 768w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/5is64ZLWFH2jHLc3fQE4o6-415-80.jpg 415w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/5is64ZLWFH2jHLc3fQE4o6-360-80.jpg 360w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/5is64ZLWFH2jHLc3fQE4o6-320-80.jpg 320w\" sizes=\"(min-width: 710px) 670px, calc(100vw - 30px)\" loading=\"lazy\" data-original-mos=\"https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/5is64ZLWFH2jHLc3fQE4o6.jpg\" data-pin-media=\"https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/5is64ZLWFH2jHLc3fQE4o6.jpg\"/\u003e\u003c/picture\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\n\u003cdiv\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003eThe Shuffle Modular Table by Mia Hamborg is beautfully lacquered, giving it its iconic glossy finish. The structure of this table is stunning - it looks like a child\u0026#39;s abacus, but remains stylish.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003c/div\u003e\n\u003c/div\u003e\u003ch2 id=\"section-diy-advice\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003eDIY advice\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/h2\u003e\u003cp\u003eSeeing successful DIY projects can encourage you to give it a go yourself, and this isn’t something you should shy away from - just ensure you are practising DIY safely.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e‘I really appreciate the creativity behind making your own designer dupes at home. To ensure your furniture is built safely, start by investing in sturdy materials that can withstand wear and tear,’ says Josh Qian, Co-Founder of\u003ca data-analytics-id=\"inline-link\" href=\"https://www.bestonlinecabinets.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\" data-url=\"https://www.bestonlinecabinets.com/\" referrerpolicy=\"no-referrer-when-downgrade\" data-hl-processed=\"none\"\u003e Best Online Cabinets\u003c/a\u003e.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003eFind a design you love and break it down into its essential components. Identify key features such as the style, finish, and hardware that make it stand out. Then, source materials that closely match your inspiration.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e‘Visiting local hardware stores can provide insights into trending materials or finishes that might add a unique twist to your project.\u0026#39;\u003c/p\u003e\u003cfigure data-bordeaux-image-check=\"\"\u003e\u003cdiv\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/oK9a9ccsCWND9i5QGdkW9P-320-80.gif\" alt=\"Turquoise trolley\" srcset=\"https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/oK9a9ccsCWND9i5QGdkW9P-1920-80.gif 1920w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/oK9a9ccsCWND9i5QGdkW9P-1600-80.gif 1600w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/oK9a9ccsCWND9i5QGdkW9P-1280-80.gif 1280w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/oK9a9ccsCWND9i5QGdkW9P-1024-80.gif 1024w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/oK9a9ccsCWND9i5QGdkW9P-768-80.gif 768w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/oK9a9ccsCWND9i5QGdkW9P-415-80.gif 415w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/oK9a9ccsCWND9i5QGdkW9P-360-80.gif 360w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/oK9a9ccsCWND9i5QGdkW9P-320-80.gif 320w\" sizes=\"(min-width: 710px) 670px, calc(100vw - 30px)\" loading=\"lazy\" data-original-mos=\"https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/oK9a9ccsCWND9i5QGdkW9P.gif\" data-pin-media=\"https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/oK9a9ccsCWND9i5QGdkW9P.gif\"/\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003cp\u003e(Image credit: Future PLC / Colin Poole)\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\u003cp\u003e‘As you build, take your time with each step, measuring twice for accuracy and ensuring that joints are secure,\u0026#39; advises Josh. \u0026#39;For finishes, experimenting with paint or stains can help you achieve that designer look. Don’t hesitate to consult online tutorials or local workshops for additional tips and techniques.\u0026#39;\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e‘Document your process. Take photos as you build, noting challenges and solutions. This will help you refine your techniques and create a valuable resource to share with others in the DIY community.\u0026#39;\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003e‘Enjoy the process, and you’ll create beautiful pieces and gain valuable skills along the way!\u0026#39;\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003eDon\u0026#39;t be afraid of trying something new, recreating this designer dupe could be a great way of spending a rainy Sunday.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003eWhat will you create?\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003c/div\u003e\u003c/div\u003e",
